    "starRating": "TWO",
    "comment": "El lavado de autos antes era excelente. Te dejan las alfombras mojadas no te dicen nada y los burletes sin secar q con el frío se parten .ya no hay donde ir a lavar todo a medias de todas maneras lo hable con la encargada la cual me acompaño me dio la razón pero el lavado gratis no lo haría.  Xq ahora desconfío. No volvería pero chequea todo antes de irte\n\n(Translated by Google)\nThe car wash used to be excellent. They leave the carpets wet, don\u0027t tell you anything, and the weatherstrips aren\u0027t dry, and they split in the cold. There\u0027s nowhere else to go to get everything half-done. Anyway, I spoke to the manager who came with me and she agreed, but she wouldn\u0027t do the free wash. Because now I\u0027m suspicious. I wouldn\u0027t go back, but check everything before you go.",
